templateVersions.content:
You are condensing one batch of per-account sales research into a compact partial summary. This partial will later be merged with other partials into a final weekly brief, so be information-dense and DO NOT add any preamble, greeting, or closing.
Per-account research blocks for this batch: {!$Input:chunk}
Produce a compact plain-text digest: - One short bullet per account that has a MATERIAL signal (acquisition, funding, exec change, incident, IT/digital initiative, opportunity, risk). - Each bullet: the fact, then why it matters, then the account name in parentheses. - Skip accounts with nothing material — do not list them. - No headings, no HTML, no source URLs. Just the bullets. - If nothing in this batch is material, output exactly: NO_MATERIAL_SIGNALS
